description:
On my last week before leaving Dubai I finally visited the Burj Khalifa, the tallest building in the world. After being one of the first to go up before the sunlight, I was exhausted by the time I got down later that morning. Walking around the area outside of the Dubai Mall towards the Dubai Opera, this interesting metal sculpture caught my eye. 

Minimal edits were made to the image aside from light/dark curve adjustments, yellow saturation and sharpness edits.
